            ],
            "correct_response": [
                [
                    "3"
                ]
            ],
            "solution": "<div><B>Solution: <br>Correct\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAnswer : <b>3</B>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div><b>As per data, 30 minutes gain is happening in 144 hrs. It would have taken 72\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thours for 15 minutes gain. On Thursday\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tat 1 pm, it would be 5 mins ahead.</div></div>"
